Krita is a free and open-source digital painting application that is widely used by artists for creating illustrations, concept art, textures, comics, and animations. It is designed to provide a powerful and intuitive toolset for both beginners and professional artists. Krita offers a range of features such as brush engines, layer management, vector tools, and color management, making it a versatile choice for digital artwork. It is available on Windows, macOS, and Linux platforms.
